in.definex.NetworkJob

Class NetworkJobManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.definex.NetworkJob.NetworkJobManager

  • public class NetworkJobManager
extends java.lang.Object
    NetworkJobManager Manages a list of NetworkJob, when a NetworkJob is requested, via add method a request string is created and sent to the service. after the service returns a response, the NetworkJob with specified id is searched and its response is handled for more info, read NetworkJob.java
